00:51:14,280 --> 00:51:21,280
 So that is kind of the, and I guess it's a bit of also the, where the endogeneity comes in.

426
00:51:21,280 --> 00:51:25,280
 And when you, now I'm going to mention this once, when you mentioned the endogeneity of R*,

427
00:51:25,280 --> 00:51:29,280
 I guess I could mention also the fact that we had these financial boom and busts.

